      "[Schoolhouse, West Lawn]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Framed by colorful rows of sunset marigolds and woolflowers, a slender pathway of crushed cobblestone wends its way through the manicured lawn of vibrant green grass to and from a small greenhouse and the schoolhouse.  Glowing lanterns dangle from shepherd's crooks fashioned of wrought iron, their soft lamplight causing the stone to glimmer.  Stretching its limbs to create a sheltering shade, a mottled dogwood tree grows in the center of the southern lawn and is laden with colorful blossoms."
    ],
